## childMessage.directive.js

**Summary:** Directive (element: "childMessage") rendering a reply/child message within a forum thread. Displays sender avatar, name, ranking stars, formatted send date, and message content.

**Dependencies:**
- app/app/contact/forums/forum.module.js — registered on forumModule

**Tags:** forum, communication, directive, ui

**Implementation:** app/app/contact/forums/message/childMessage/childMessage.directive.js
